  <brief_title>Efficacy Emollient on Xerosis in Children With Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of the V0034CR01B Emollient on Xerosis in Children With Atopic Dermatitis. Randomised, Vehicle-controlled, Parallel-groups, Double-blind Study With an Open Label Extension.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
