  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Presenting with atopic dermatitis, dry skin, objective SCORAD &lt; 15,

          -  With xerosis on the body and a xerosis score &gt; = 2 (SCORAD sub-score) on the anterior
             part of lower limbs,

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute phase of atopic dermatitis

          -  Severe form of atopic dermatitis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
